  "texts": [
    "In the case of zero-shot results, both 0-M1 and 0-M2 most commonly did not reference any abstracts in their responses: 527 occurrences (58% of all the answers) for 0-M1 and 165 for 0-M2 (18.2% of all the answers).",
    "M1 and M2 did not reference any abstracts in 8 (0.9%) and 5 (0.5%) answers, respectively.",
    "By manual inspection of these answers, the models stated that none of the abstracts were relevant, demonstrating their proficiency in task execution.",
    "On the other hand, in most of the answers without references 0-M1 and 0-M2 answered the question but without providing any references to their statements.",
    "Additionally, some 0-M2's answers (35 of them) repeated the first part of the instruction, suggesting the need for further postprocessing of its answers."
